summary: SummaryHighlightsClean IngredientsSustainable PackagingGive BackELEMIS Pro-Collagen Cleansing Balm is a 3-in-1 melting cleanser that easily removes makeup, daily visible pollutants and impurities for a soft and glowing complexion.
details: DetailsBenefitsThis No.1 best-seller transforms into 3 unique textures for the ultimate cleansing experience: it nourishes as a balm, easily removes makeup as a cleansing oil and hydrates as a cleansing milk.Its unique blend of 9 essential oils including Lavender, Chamomile and Eucalyptus smell like heaven in a jar to invigorate the senses.Formulated without mineral oils, it also combines Rose and Mimosa waxes with Elderberry, Starflower and Optimega Oils.Skin is left feeling deeply cleansed, soothed and supremely soft.Research Results96% of users felt the product helped leave their skin feeling softened and soothed.*94% of users agreed that the product helped leave their skin feeling clean.*90% of users felt the product was effective at removing make-up.*Independent User Trials 2012. Results based on 54 people over 2 weeks.Item 2533942How To UseWarm into the palms and then massage over the face, neck and décolleté with light circular massage movements. Moisten fingertips and continue to massage. Gently wipe away warm, damp cotton cleansing cloth. For maximum absorption and deep cleansing, enjoy whilst in a warm bath. Balm may melt when warm but resets perfectly when cooled. Avoid contact with eyes.IngredientsPrunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Caprylic/Capric Triglyceride, PEG-6 Caprylic/Capric Glycerides, PEG-8 Beeswax, Cetearyl Alcohol, Sorbitan Stearate, Sambucus Nigra (Elderberry) Seed Oil, PEG-60 Almond Glycerides, Silica, Avena Sativa (Oat) Kernel Oil, Triticum Vulgare (Wheat) Germ Oil, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis (Orange) Peel Cera (Wax), Glycerin, Lecithin, Padina Pavonica Thallus Extract, Borago Officinalis (Starflower) Seed Oil, Lavandula Angustifolia (Lavender) Oil, Phenoxyethanol, Linalool, Acacia Decurrens (Mimosa) Flower Wax, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil, Rosa Multiflora (Rose) Flower Cera (Wax), Lavandula Hybrida (Lavandin) Oil, Pelargonium Graveolens (Geranium) Flower Oil, Geraniol, Eucalyptus Globulus Leaf Oil, Tocopherol, Anthemis Nobilis (Chamomile) Flower Oil, Citronellol, Cinnamomum Camphora (Ho Wood) Wood Oil, Limonene, Mentha Arvensis (Mint) Leaf Oil, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis (Orange) Oil, Fragrance (Parfum), Vitis Vinifera (Grape) Seed Oil, Menthol, Eugenia Caryophyllus (Clove) Leaf Oil, Citric Acid.Shipping & Coupon RestrictionsThis brand is excluded from most Ulta Beauty coupons.See brand eligibility details
how_to_use: Warm into the palms and then massage over the face, neck and décolleté with light circular massage movements. Moisten fingertips and continue to massage. Gently wipe away warm, damp cotton cleansing cloth. For maximum absorption and deep cleansing, enjoy whilst in a warm bath. Balm may melt when warm but resets perfectly when cooled. Avoid contact with eyes.

reviews.headline: Exactly what I wanted
reviews.comments: Incredible product

reviews.headline: Cleans makeup and isn't difficult to wash off
reviews.comments: LOVE THIS! Other oily cleansers tend to stay on the skin after washing off with water. This does wash off with warm water and doesn't irritate my eyes. My skin feels smooth after. If I want a smoother finish, I use a clean washcloth to help exfoliate my skin. It helps to double cleanse after as well.

reviews.headline: i got this thinking i would like it
reviews.comments: The smell is so overpowering that I couldn't even use it twice. I got the black cherry one, and no, thank you, will not be repurchasing.

reviews.headline: Great
reviews.comments: I like this cleansing balm from Elemis so much more than their original. It does a great job of removing makeup, sunscreen, skincare, and oil and I use it at night. Gifted to me by Elemis and I would recommend!

reviews.headline: Pricey but love it!
reviews.comments: Love how this truly melts my makeup off and LOVE the cherry!!!

reviews.headline: the best skin prep for makeup
reviews.comments: I bought the fragrance-free version because my skin is super sensitive. Used it as directed and wiped away with a damp cloth(a wet paper towel because that's all I had) and WOW. What a difference it made in my skin. It was so plush and plump after using this . I have very textured, sensitive, acne-prone skin and this works AMAZING as a primer. My makeup laid so flawlessly and that's very hard to do with texture So this product is a win for me.  I highly recommend this for my textured skin girlies, specifically the fragrance-free one!

reviews.headline: It is gentle and effective
reviews.comments: I loved the effectiveness of it but I didn't quite enjoy the scent of it. It smelled like a medicine I have come across before. It is feels very good on my combination skin and the smell is a bit strange but I don't mind too much. Complimentary from elemis.

reviews.headline: Cherry
reviews.comments: hands down one of the most indulgent skincare products I've ever used. If you love the original balm, this version is a treat same rich, buttery texture but has a black cherry scent this cleansing is a must have! Gifted by elemis

reviews.headline: Stings my eyes
reviews.comments: I'd buy this again but in the fragrance free version. My eyes aren't overly sensitive but there's something (I'm guessing the essential oils) that my eyes don't agree with. It stings my eyes if I get too close with it. So I'm using a separate micellar water to remove eye makeup. I'll use this up but would not buy the original version again. If your eyes can tolerate it, it's lovely, feels luxurious on the skin, removes all my makeup easily, and rinses clean without making my skin feel stripped and tight.

reviews.headline: My Skin Has Never Felt This Clean and Soft!
reviews.comments: I don't wear makeup, but this balm leaves my skin feeling incredibly clean, soft, and hydrated. It removes dirt and impurities without drying me out, and I love that it's fragrance-free and gentle. This is the only cleanser I use now—my skin has never felt better!

reviews.headline: OBSESSED
reviews.comments: I've always loved the Elemis cleansing balm but the black cherry smells so so so incredible. It takes off your makeup SOOOOO good. I love to use this when I'm wearing waterproof makeup or just a lot in general. I have a combination type of skin type. gifted by Elemis thank you I'm obsessed.

reviews.headline: In love!!
reviews.comments: This balm melts like butter into oil, left my skin skin soft, hydrated, and not stripped. The scent had notes of black cherry and almond, definitely an acquired taste, but I loved it. Gifted by Elemis.

reviews.headline: Removes makeup.
reviews.comments: Elemis effectively removes all types of makeup, including waterproof products. I use it whenever I wear my waterproof eyeliner, and it completely takes it off. I always follow up with a double cleanse when I use this product, and I haven't experienced any issues. It doesn't dry out my skin; instead, it leaves my skin feeling fresh and clean. Plus, it has an amazing scent! I am extremely satisfied with the results. Gifted by elemis

reviews.headline: Still a favorite!
reviews.comments: Still a favorite! Love how they have different version of this balm, scent wise, but the formula is still perfect every time! Melts away every bit of makeup without harsh tugging or rubbing, emulsifies beautifully into a milky lather & rinses without residue or an oily finish. Perfect first cleanse & the jar is a generous amount! My skin feels clean & ready for the rest of my routine. (gifted by Elemis in exchange for honest review)

reviews.headline: Would purchase again!
reviews.comments: I am in love with this cleansing balm! It really takes all of your makeup off so it's a one step cleanser for sure. It also will last a long time because you don't need much to get a nice clean. Will purchase again! Gifted by elemis

reviews.headline: Melts away makeup
reviews.comments: I like using this product on days where I wear a lot of makeup or feel like I need a deep cleanse. It does a great job at melting away dirt, debris, and makeup off my skin without irritation. I tend to cleanse again after to remove any residue. Gifted by Elemis

reviews.headline: Cleans, hydrates & smells amazing'
reviews.comments: This black cherry cleansing balms was complimentary from Elemis. I have been using this for about two weeks now and love it! Helps to remove my makeup after a full day at the office. It leaves the skin feeling clean and feeling hydrated. The black cherry scent adds a warm, subtly sweet almost floral scent without being too overpowering. Can't say enough good things about this product! Highly recommend!

reviews.headline: soo good
reviews.comments: I received this product complimentary from Elemis in exchange for my honest review. I think this balm is so good. It removes makeup with ease and leaves your skin feeling great. It is the perfect first step in cleansing. The only thing is i wasn't a huge fan of the scent at first but it's grown on me and isn't an issue. I would see if you like the smell though

reviews.headline: The best ever!
reviews.comments: I mean, it's iconic for a reason. This is the best cleansing balm on the market, it cuts through even waterproof mascara with no stinging in my eyes! It's smells delicious as a bonus, gifted by Elemis.

reviews.headline: Spa in a jar!
reviews.comments: If you're looking for a cleansing balm that feels indulgent, smells like a spa in a jar, and melts away makeup while delivering hydration, the Pro-Collagen Black Cherry Cleansing Balm is a standout. It's particularly well-suited for dryer or mature skin types, and anyone who enjoys fragrance-rich skincare experiences. However, if you're sensitive to scent, have oily or acne-prone skin, or prefer a cleanser that rinses completely residue‑free, you may want to patch-test first or explore fragrance‑free or lighter alternatives. Gifted by Elemis beauty

faceoff_positive.comments: I dont write reviews too often,so when I do,its because a product stood out to me! I receive the Elemis Pro-Collagen Cleansing Balm as a sample,so I wasn't really familiar with this product. I used it as directed and I was immediately impressed with the results,my skin was left so soft,and dewy looking! This is such an amazing cleasing balm,but it can be used as an overnight mask as well,which I tried it out as,and I loved it!! I will now be using this as part of my daily skincare regimen! I highly suggest you try this cleansing balm/overnight mask!
faceoff_positive.headline: Skin is so soft

faceoff_negative.comments: There is no way the reviews on this website are legitimate. This product is absolutely horrible. It does NOT remove makeup as advertised. It also has a strange smell to it. I reached out to customer support to see if they had any recommendations and they told me that this is not intended to remove eye makeup and then proceeded to recommend TWO other products I should be using on top of this if I actually want to remove my makeup. Lots of false advertising and then they were zero help beyond attempting to get me to spend even more of my money on their products. RUN far away from this product and this company.
faceoff_negative.headline: They must be paying people for reviews.
